{"tid":2291210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"侵律師林伍德再次證實美軍曾經搜查德國Scytl設施","createTime":"2020-11-18T14:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T23:07:49.000Z","uid":154486,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bac0e625fee6c76787d3101a5ae8e0170baa4c38","tid":2291210,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T14:47:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Qb71Gb_O7Yw?t=158\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQb71Gb_O7Yw%3Ft%3D158&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5sWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=571e594a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Qb71Gb_O7Yw?t=158</a><br />\n<br />\nLin Wood已經再次清楚證實左<br />\n「美軍係Scytl法蘭克福設施攞到Server資料」<br />\n但係佢冇透露係唔係CIA<br />\n<br />\n證明左之前Solomon Yue既Comment係岩<br />\n【突發】Solomon Yue： 美 軍 係 德 國 攞 Server 單 野 係 真<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2288853\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2288853</a><br />\n<br />\n唯一矛盾之處係Solomon之前條link講係個設施同Scytl無關<br />\n<br />\n佢之後有講大部分我地已經清楚既Smartmatic，Dominion同Scytl之間既關係，<br />\n最尾一提索羅斯就斷左一陣線，詳細討論係另一個巴打既post︰<br />\n美國大選舞弊：相信已經越嚟越接近真相<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2291160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2291160</a>"},{"pid":"e6837299a373d0789daf36f5be85a4927ab3c395","tid":2291210,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T14:53:46.000Z","msg":"推post推post"},{"pid":"684032d04c70675a12e063224a0ccf42212e1912","tid":2291210,"uid":25468,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T15:06:30.000Z","msg":"可能 CIA 同 Scytl 係兩個 case"},{"pid":"be526a4952c0a1cda01c3f0b90bd1e2681034a63","tid":2291210,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T15:07:33.000Z","msg":"Fact check 左未"},{"pid":"fc27632c7bfce851dd03854ad2ed0daec0047be3","tid":2291210,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T15:08:13.000Z","msg":"最緊要有冇料先"},{"pid":"631c43e0e74e2b92a7ba752a4270b2b55a8171a7","tid":2291